00:03:51,950 --> 00:03:54,900
 Is she going through something? 

58
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:03,580
Hello, Elder Uncle. It's Tong Tong. I—

59
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:16,100
Hello, Auntie.

60
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:17,300
It's Tong Tong.

61
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:19,380
 I know your mother's brother is in trouble. 

62
00:04:19,380 --> 00:04:21,300
 He wants the loan repaid two years early, 

63
